<p><strong>No</strong> — that's the core promise of DajPrezent.pl.</p>
<p>The list owner only ever sees the gift status: "available", "reserved", "received". Your email and name (if you provided one) are never shown to them.</p>
<p>The identity of the giver is only revealed when you actually hand over the gift — that's part of the "wow" surprise effect.</p>
<p>If a gift has already been reserved by another guest, the card shows "Reserved 💗" instead of the reserve button, so duplicates are avoided.</p>
